      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p>A Free Soak allows the character make a Soak roll without having to spend a Benny. Using a Free Soak does not count as spending a Benny and does not trigger Edges that use Bennies. A character can have a maximum of one Free Soak at any given time.</p>"
